columns.claygent_prompt:
ROLE: Hiring intelligence analyst.

Scan LinkedIn jobs page + their /careers page for {company_name}.

Return JSON: {"total_open_roles": int, "roles_in_function": {"sales": int, "engineering": int, "marketing": int, "ops": int, "other": int}, "hottest_role": "string (most repeated or most senior)", "signal": "hiring_aggressively|steady|hiring_freeze|unknown"}

ROLE: Leadership team mapper.

For {company_name}, identify the current C-suite + relevant VPs in {{TARGET_FUNCTIONS}}.

Return JSON: {"executives": [{"name": "", "title": "", "linkedin_url": "", "tenure_months": int|null, "is_new_hire_lt_6mo": bool}]}

ROLE: Competitive analyst.

For {company_name}, identify their direct competitors in {{COMPETITIVE_SPACE}}.

Return JSON: {"top_competitors": [{"name": "", "competitive_angle": "string (1 sentence on how they overlap)"}], "current_vendor": "string|unknown (who they currently use in {{TOOL_CATEGORY}}, if discoverable)"}

ROLE: Risk scanner.

For {company_name}, check for: recent layoffs (last 12mo), exec departures (last 6mo), restructuring announcements, regulatory issues, or public criticism.

Return JSON: {"risk_flags": [{"flag": "", "date": "YYYY-MM-DD", "url": "", "severity": "low|medium|high"}], "overall_risk_level": "low|medium|high"}

ROLE: Account entry strategist.

Given everything we now know about {company_name}, propose THE single best entry point for {{OUR_PRODUCT_CATEGORY}}.

INPUTS:
- Strategic priorities: {strategic_priorities.priorities}
- Recent news: {recent_news_90d.items}
- Hiring signal: {hiring_posture.signal}
- New execs (<6mo): {leadership_team.executives where is_new_hire_lt_6mo = true}
- Competitive context: {competitive_context}
- Risk signals: {risk_signals.risk_flags}

Return JSON:
{
  "entry_point": {
    "who_to_target": "name + title from leadership_team",
    "why_them": "string (1 sentence)",
    "opening_angle": "string (15-25 words — the actual conversation starter)",
    "timing_rationale": "string (why now, tied to a specific signal)",
    "confidence": "high|medium|low"
  }
}
